ndnis des digitalen Abstiegs beruht.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2022) 4aAufklärung. 4aCancel Culture. 4aDigitale Medien. 4aDigitalisierung. 4aDoomscrolling. 4aInformationstechnologie. 4aInternet. 4aKrypto-Kunst. 4aMedien. 4aMediensoziologie. 4aMedienwissenschaft. 4aNFT. 4aNetzkritik. 4aPlattform. 4aPlattformökonomie. 4aPsychische Gesundheit. 4aSocial Media. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Media Studies.2bisacsh  aDigital Media.  aDigitalization.  aEnlightenment.  aInformation Technology.  aInternet.  aMedia Studies.  aMedia.  aNet Critique.  aPlatform Economy.  aSociology of Media.1 aIlyes, Petra, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aTheodor, Jennifer Sophia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2z978311076700108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Sociology 2022z9783110994520oZDB-23-DSL40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839463338?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839463338423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839463338/original  a978-3-11-076700-1  DG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2b2022  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2022  aZDB-23-DSLb2022